#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.log10.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.log10"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log10.log10:1 of
msgid "Return the base 10 logarithm of the input tensor, element-wise."
msgstr "返回输入张量的以 10 为底的对数，逐元素计算。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log10.log10 of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log10.log10:3 of
msgid "Input values."
msgstr "输入值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log10.log10:5 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须可以广播到输入形状。如果未提供或"
"为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（仅可作为关键字参数）的长度必须"
"等于输出数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log10.log10:10 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log10.log10 of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log10.log10:15 of
msgid ""
"**y** -- The logarithm to the base 10 of `x`, element-wise. NaNs are "
"returned where x is negative."
msgstr "**y** -- `x` 的以 10 为底的对数，逐元素计算。当 `x` 为负数时返回 NaN。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log10.log10 of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log10.log10:20 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log10.log10:21 of
msgid ""
"Logarithm is a multivalued function: for each `x` there is an infinite "
"number of `z` such that `10**z = x`. The convention is to return the `z` "
"whose imaginary part lies in `[-pi, pi]`."
msgstr ""
"对数是一个多值函数：对于每个 `x`，存在无限多个 `z` 使得 `10**z = x`。约定"
"返回虚部在 `[-pi, pi]` 范围内的 `z`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log10.log10:25 of
msgid ""
"For real-valued input data types, `log10` always returns real output. For"
" each value that cannot be expressed as a real number or infinity, it "
"yields ``nan`` and sets the `invalid` floating point error flag."
msgstr ""
"对于实数类型的输入数据，`log10` 总是返回实数输出。对于无法表示为实数或"
"无穷大的值，它将返回 ``nan`` 并设置 `invalid` 浮点错误标志。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log10.log10:29 of
msgid ""
"For complex-valued input, `log10` is a complex analytical function that "
"has a branch cut `[-inf, 0]` and is continuous from above on it. `log10` "
"handles the floating-point negative zero as an infinitesimal negative "
"number, conforming to the C99 standard."
msgstr ""
"对于复数类型的输入，`log10` 是一个具有分支切割 `[-inf, 0]` 的复解析函数，"
"并在其上从上方连续。`log10` 将浮点负零处理为无穷小的负数，符合 C99 标准。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log10.log10:35 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log10.log10:36 of
msgid ""
"M. Abramowitz and I.A. Stegun, \"Handbook of Mathematical Functions\", "
"10th printing, 1964, pp. 67. http://www.math.sfu.ca/~cbm/aands/"
msgstr ""
"M. Abramowitz 和 I.A. Stegun，《数学函数手册》，第 10 次印刷，1964 年，第"
" 67 页。http://www.math.sfu.ca/~cbm/aands/"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.log10.log10:38 of
msgid "Wikipedia, \"Logarithm\". http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Logarithm"
msgstr "维基百科，“对数”。http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Logarithm"

